This project links the MariaDB Connector/C (vendored as the git submodule
libs/mariadb-connector-c), which is licensed under the GNU Lesser General Public
License, version 2.1 (LGPL-2.1). The LGPL applies to that connector only, not to
this project's MIT-licensed code. Because the connector is statically linked,
LGPL-2.1 §6 requires that recipients be able to relink the combined work against
a modified connector. This is satisfied by distributing the connector's complete
source (the pinned submodule at
https://github.com/mariadb-corporation/mariadb-connector-c) alongside the
component; the project's own object files can be provided on request to enable
relinking. See NOTICE.md.
